@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - UC039 ViewAdminDashboard

actor "Admin" as Actor
boundary "DashboardUI" as UI
control "AdminController" as Controller
entity "SystemDB" as Entity

Actor -> UI : 1. Truy cập trang chủ Dashboard Admin
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 2. getOverviewStats()
activate Controller
Controller -> Entity : 3. querySystemMetrics()
activate Entity
Entity --> Controller : 4. return metrics (users, recipes, active rate)
deactivate Entity
Controller --> UI : 5. return metricsData
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 6. Hiển thị Dashboard (Số liệu tổng quan, Biểu đồ)
deactivate UI
@enduml
